export const homePageReviews = [
  {
    author: "Joy S.",
    source: "Yelp",
    URL:
      "https://www.yelp.com/biz/zhou-agency-chicago?hrid=gymhJw6KTWlXE0ea7Sb00A&utm_campaign=www_review_share_popup&utm_medium=copy_link&utm_source=(direct)",
    content:
      "Taxed time is no longer high Anxiety time for me this agency is the most professional honest and caring agency I have ever done business with the entire staff are very welcoming. Most important is they are smart and good at what they. At the invitation of Zhou Agency I just completed my 2019 pre tax review. This is wonderful, I have a good idea of what I can expect( news not so good) and I like that and fully prepared. They are truly a company that cares about their clients who integrity and professionalism is top notch. Keep up the good work Zhou God Bless the entire team",
    numStars: 5
  },
  {
    author: "Zheng Z.",
    source: "Yelp",
    URL: "",
    content:
      "It was a very pleasant experience working with them. Very professional and efficient. Ms. Zhou helped us figure out all tax forms needed in a very short time. Would like to work with them again in the future.",
    numStars: 5
  },
  {
    author: "Jie Z.",
    source: "Yelp",
    URL: "",
    content:
      "Justine and her agency did outstanding job to educate clients for knowledges  and did fantastic job for their field of service. I have participated few of their seminars and was WOW by their professionalism and knowledges of Realestate and Tax field. Keep up the great work Justine and surely I am looking forward to working with you and your colleagues..",
    numStars: 5
  }
];
